{"tid":2309330,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"時光倒流一句話 好撚正呀屌你老味","createTime":"2020-12-02T12:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T03:08:07.000Z","uid":307910,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8c4c839875c70553d03e2a6052b359b89c3d8d35","tid":2309330,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"呢首歌真係寫得好深入個心 將嗰種失落同尷尬嘅感覺寫晒出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我不必   異能大到   可扭曲真相改春秋<br />\n我只想  忘掉你  不解這溫柔   斷言未接受<br />\n<br />\n其實我只想    未曾笨到    搞不清楚你    先開口<br />\n我只想    忘掉你    聽到的表情    像很荒謬<br />\n難題是    時光未許倒流    明日只可向下流<br />\n尷尬到自己的人    假設還未夠狠    反了臉出走<br />\n厚面皮些    演好友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我兩樣都做晒 係咪好勁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4871ea5b117c9a2d6f7f5330cc49207e5d7c18c","tid":2309330,"uid":308264,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:57:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"495491a8424a05174fd31e5daaed610944fa546e","tid":2309330,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b4871ea5b117c9a2d6f7f5330cc49207e5d7c18c","tid":2309330,"uid":308264,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:57:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025091b87e82ff5bf290823f9525dc76b2018a42","tid":2309330,"uid":37197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:09:18.000Z","msg":"好鍾意<br />\n如果我有逆轉的超能力<br />\n情願你有讀心的超能力<br />\n<br />\n果句既音樂好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3526d8485049eb2eb351ed2ed37e99d5d4c098f6","tid":2309330,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T19:11:30.000Z","msg":"家謙老師<i